PostProcessor

public PostProcessor(PreProcessor prePro,
                     java.util.List<CHS> CHSList,
                     int gapNum)
Create a new PostProcessor object and calculate statistics for each CHS.

参数：
prePro - the PreProcessor object for corresponding CHS searching
CHSList - a list containing all searched CHS
gapNum - the maximum gap (gene number) allowed between neighboring genes
方法详细信息

getGeneList

public Gene[][] getGeneList(CHS iCHS)
Get gene lists linked in the CHS.

参数：
iCHS - a CHS object
返回：
a two dimensional array with four rows. The first row contains all genes in GenoLoc A and the second row in GenoLoc B; the third row contains matched genes in GenoLoc A and the fourth row in genoLoc B; the genes in the third and fourth rows are matched.
